import * as React from 'react';
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';
import {Button, TextField, Typography} from '@mui/material';



export const MainPage =()=>{
  return(
    <Grid container
      sx={{ backgroundColor:'secondary.main', height:'100vh', width:'100vw', justifyContent:'center', alignItems:'center'}}>
      <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} key={'generate'} >

        <Grid item container xs={6} justifyContent={'center'} key={'validate'} >
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} >
            <Typography variant={'h1'} style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              {'Generate Token'}
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} >
            <Typography variant={'h2'} style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              {'This section allows you to create a new token based on your chosen digits. Customize the available digits and click "Generate" to create a token.'}
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} style={{ marginTop: '50px' }}  >
            <TextField id="outlined-basic" label="XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX" variant="outlined" sx={{ width: '400px' }} />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} style={{ marginTop: '20px' }} >
            <Button variant="contained" >Validate</Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>


        <Grid item container xs={6} justifyContent={'center'}  >
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'}>
            <Typography variant={'h1'}>
              {'Validate Token'}
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} marginTop={'150px'}  >
            <TextField id="outlined-basic" label="XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX" variant="outlined"  sx={{width:'400px'}} />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} marginTop={'30px'} >
            <Button variant="contained" >Generate</Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  );
 }
